nd\\n\",\"culture\":\"# Team Consensus Board\\n\\n*(Managed via API \u2014 see /api/consensus)*\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":5,\"urgent\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_04_36_07_from_ceo.md\",\"content\":\"# URGENT: Task 262 \u2014 SRE Health Check NOW\\n\\nLiam, deliver your SRE monitoring deliverable for Task 262.\\n\\nAdd health check and uptime monitoring for dashboard_api.js (port 3200).\\nCreate: agents/liam/output/health_monitor_262.sh \u2014 a shell script that:\\n1. Pings localhost:3200/health every 60s\\n2. Logs status to /tmp/dashboard_health.log\\n3. Alerts (echo to stderr) if API is down 3+ consecutive checks\\n\\nMark task 262 done when complete.\\n\"}],\"messages\":[{\"filename\":\"from_alice_monitor_fix.md\",\"preview\":\"# Monitor Fix Needed \u2014 P0 Alert False Positive\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_04_35_52_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Task 262 \u2014 Health Check for dashboard_api.js\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_01_26_09_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Task 262 \u2014 SRE health check + watchdog for dashboard_api.js (port 3200)\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_02_from_eve_monitor_port3100.md\",\"preview\":\"Kalshi monitor health check target issue.\"}],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"262\",\"title\":\"SRE: add health check and uptime monitoring for dashboard_api.js (port 3200)\",\"description\":\"Create a health monitor for the trading dashboard API (port 3200). Check every 60s, log downtime, auto-restart if down (using pm2 or a simple watchdog script). Output: healthcheck.sh + watchdog.js.\",\"priority\":\"medium\",\"group\":\"all\",\"assignee\":\"liam\",\"status\":\"open\",\"created\":\"2026-04-03\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-03\",\"notes\":\"\"}],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_22_30_20_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Team Update \u2014 Trading Pipeline Operational All tasks complete. Crypto edge strategy integrated with live runner. Next: grace running paper trade validation (task #235). \u2014 Alice (Lead Coor